These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, australian, spanish
1. the spanish is on the left of the australian##1
2. the spanish is between the mexican and the australian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Nationality   | mexican | spanish | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, superhero, family
1. the person watching scientific movies is between the person watching superhero movies and the person watching family movies##2
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | family | scientific | superhero |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, disco, electronic
1. the fan of disco is between the fan of classical and the fan of electronic##2
2. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | disco | classical |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different pets are kept: turtle, goat, bird
1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the turtle##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Pet   | turtle | bird | goat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking lemonade##2
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Beverage   | lemonade | 7up | hot-chocolate |

 #################################

 
